  "detailed_description": "Beat waves and waves of monsters to get stronger, in this clicker-like adventure!<br>Before entering each new wave you have to beat the boss from the previous one!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681260/extras/b29fba805ddec8323148723178be538b.poster.avif?t=1726266375\" width=622 height=554 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681260/extras/b29fba805ddec8323148723178be538b.webm?t=1726266375\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681260/extras/b29fba805ddec8323148723178be538b.mp4?t=1726266375\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Buy new weapons, on the shop, smash stronger monsters with your new weapons to get stronger loot!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681260/extras/190f25b1c49222e170481694e962fb8b.poster.avif?t=1726266375\" width=450 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681260/extras/190f25b1c49222e170481694e962fb8b.webm?t=1726266375\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681260/extras/190f25b1c49222e170481694e962fb8b.mp4?t=1726266375\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Buy upgrades from the shop to go even further into the waves<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681260/extras/1da127efd1859eb4d28f44fdbc02265d.poster.avif?t=1726266375\" width=466 height=674 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2681260/extras/1da127efd1859eb4d28f44f